{"tid":795213,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"夏神：車仔係唔會放棄","createTime":"2018-08-26T22:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T01:35:32.000Z","uid":153600,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d64799caf4ef91f452125845281b4f8eae068d8","tid":795213,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T22:44:38.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ZGIDNEE%2FQoc1KCe8%2F31F0J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=29455a23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英超勁旅車路士作客險勝紐卡素2:1，贏波功臣夏薩特拍心口直言：「車仔係永遠唔會放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n車路士完場前3分鐘，憑烏龍球全取3分，比賽最佳球員夏薩特（Eden Hazard）高興表示：「當紐卡素完場前追平，或許每個人都在想，比賽可能以和為貴，但我們是車路士，所以一定不會放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n「己隊表現可圈可點，全場比賽創造了很多入球機會，贏波是實至名歸，但大家為了3分，賽後也都很疲累。」夏神補充道。<br />\n<br />\n不得不提，博到12碼兼製造烏龍球的馬高斯阿朗素，同樣應記一功，賽後被問到極刑判決是否正確時，他斬釘截鐵表示：「一定是對的，我在對方碰到皮球前先踢到波，而非覺得有接觸之後才落地，顯然是我被他絆倒。」<br />\n<br />\n對於藍軍取得3連勝，這位西班牙人難掩興奮回應：「這是妙不可言的勝仗，3分對球隊很重要，其實，我覺得最後入球不是烏龍球，應該計入我數。」"},{"pid":"abd820a4b17c4d05ed50f1ad9debccd1e2cf7e56","tid":795213,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad713580bdeb386bfecbb081eb9eea01999d7d78","tid":795213,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"早排先話想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2cc0c2a1dffa0a4015fd329bc984816fd8653e","tid":795213,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad713580bdeb386bfecbb081eb9eea01999d7d78","tid":795213,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"早排先話想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"早排即係幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9ae45299cd9bc8122053607a93944bad71b594","tid":795213,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:24:30.000Z","msg":"梗係啦 知道球證會出手呀嗎"},{"pid":"4d669a82077b0717c29ad219ca4f15d1f69e1f9a","tid":795213,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7a2cc0c2a1dffa0a4015fd329bc984816fd8653e","tid":795213,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad713580bdeb386bfecbb081eb9eea01999d7d78","tid":795213,"uid":163937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"早排先話想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:56:14.000Z","msg":"早排即係幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:25:44.000Z","msg":"高圖斯搞9佢姐"},{"pid":"7275f3417e2f75de13ee36bb2a515adc6a26b759","tid":795213,"uid":66839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"1月味又走"}]}